  <section class="info-section">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Clean Arcade is a collection of free browser games. No ads, no tracking, no accounts. Every game runs directly in your browser — nothing to download or sign up for. Game progress and favorites are saved locally and never leave your device. Most games work on mobile. Available in 100+ languages.</p>
    <p>Feedback, game suggestions, or questions: <a href="mailto:{{ meta.email }}">{{ meta.email }}</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="info-section">
    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>We don't collect your data. All game saves, favorites, and preferences are stored in your browser's localStorage. Nothing is sent to any server.</p>
    <p>Third-party services: <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Pages</a> (hosting), <a href="https://bunny.net/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bunny Fonts</a> (web fonts), <a href="https://gtranslate.io/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GTranslate</a> (translation). No other third-party scripts.</p>
    <p>To clear all locally stored data: Developer Tools &rarr; Application &rarr; Local Storage &rarr; delete entries for this domain.</p>
  </section>

